name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 19, another intern committed suicide at the Nanning First People's Hospital

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 21, Harbin Engineering University. The school forcibly took away students’ electric bikes without their consent and without any written notice to inform the students.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, social media reported that Anhui Province's civil servants' salaries were cut and rectified, and the excess housing provident fund and a number of subsidies needed to be returned.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On the evening of March 21, someone held up a white-screen iPad at the opening of the new Apple store in Jing'an Temple, Shanghai, prompting people to take photos and cheer.
The opening event was canceled due to the large number of people on site.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
March 20, Nanning, Guangxi. A netizen posted a video saying that a shop building along Xinyang Road collapsed.
The Nanning Housing and Urban-Rural Development Bureau issued a report on the situation. After investigation and verification, the operator of "Chengzhi Hotel" was suspected of illegally demolishing the load-bearing walls of two main buildings and the auxiliary building on the evening of the 19th for business purposes, which led to the partial collapse accident. The accident did not cause any casualties.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 20, China's National Bureau of Statistics released unemployment data for age groups in February. The data showed that in February, the unemployment rate for urban workers aged 16-24, excluding students, was 15.3%; the unemployment rate for urban workers aged 25-29, excluding students, was 6.4%; the unemployment rate for urban workers aged 30-59, excluding students, was 4.2%.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, it was reported online that a senior boy from Jiangyan No. 2 Middle School in Taizhou City, Jiangsu Province, had placed a camera in the east female restroom on the fourth floor to secretly film since his sophomore year. However, because the student was a relative of the vice-principal, he was favored and even shouted in the group, "You deserve it for me to secretly film you."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Correction: The event was not cancelled, the police dispersed the crowd on the grounds that the event was over.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 21, at the Apple store in Jing'an Temple, an old lady angrily accused the people in line of worshipping foreign things. Someone asked her, "Do you know how many jobs Apple has brought to China?" She shouted, "No need, we have Huawei."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 21, in front of the People's Government of Jinghai District, Tianjin, owners of unfinished buildings waved the national flag and knelt down to defend their rights

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: It is said that the “white paper” raised at the scene was to protest against Apple’s allowing scalpers to grab the souvenir gifts, canceling the concert, and working with the police to drive away the crowd outside the venue, which disappointed the Apple fans who had waited for eight or nine hours. …
